Saving graphs

library("readxl")
Data <- read_excel("210129_Greenhouse_results.xlsx")
Data <- Data[-12]


d <- rep("06/11/20", 6)
d <- c(d, rep("11/11/20", 6))
d <- c(d, rep("18/11/20", 6))
d <- c(d, rep("30/11/20", 6))
d <- c(d, rep("14/12/20", 6))
new_date <- rep(d,8)
Data$Date2 <- new_date

Data$Date2 <- as.Date(Data$Date2, format='%d/%m/%y')


library(ggplot2)
